- cs.TL (Theoretical Computer Science) is another possible category as the paper deals with the characterization of polynomial time functions. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the representation of binary words. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with the characterization of polynomial time functions.
